      "frame": "Full Branding · Tech Services · 2020",
      "description": "UPDATE Logo Costa Unlock is a specialized software & device unlocking service — built with a complete visual identity that reflects speed, tech expertise, and digital precision. The brand system follows a dark tech aesthetic with Cyberpunk undertones, designed to perform across Telegram channels, social media, and all digital touchpoints. This is branding that earns trust in a high-stakes, fast-moving market.\n                            \nMost designers deliver a logo. Maybe a color palette. Maybe some mockups if you're lucky. This project delivers something different: a complete visual identity system for [Brand Name], explored across six visual dimensions — 3D space, Cyberpunk atmosphere, Marvel-level cinematic power, GTA street energy, motion that stops the scroll, and a storytelling framework that makes the brand feel like it's been here forever. This is not branding. This is world-building.",
